OL,3,CJeffrey Donaldson's spectacular fall
OL,4,Cfrom grace
OL,6,FSir Jeffrey Donaldson's fall from
OL,7,Fgrace has been spectacular.
OL,9,FFrom Knight of the Realm ` knighted by
OL,10,FWilliam, Prince of Wales, inside the
OL,11,Fsplendour of Buckingham Palace - to
OL,12,Fspending tonight, detained inside a
OL,13,Fstark, prison cell, held at the
OL,14,Fpleasure of His Majesty the King.
OL,16,FSir Jeffrey Donaldson will from now be
OL,17,Fknown simply by his prison number.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
