OL,3,CJeffrey Donaldson's spectacular fall
OL,4,Cfrom grace
OL,6,FWhat his trial has shown, more than
OL,7,Fanything, is that there were as one
OL,8,Fwitness in the trial said, two Jeffrey
OL,9,FDonaldsons.
OL,11,FThe pious and devout Christian who for
OL,12,Fmore than 20 years wore a fish badge
OL,13,Fon his lapel.
OL,15,FTo the watching world he wanted to
OL,16,Fportray himself as the Godly
OL,17,Fpolitician who helped lead the UK
OL,18,FPrayer for Parliament group and was
OL,19,Fthe vice-chairman of the Christians in
OL,20,FParliament All-Party Parliamentary
OL,21,FGroup at Westminster.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/5
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
