OL,3,CJeffrey Donaldson's spectacular fall
OL,4,Cfrom grace
OL,6,FHe built an image as the prayerful
OL,7,Fpolitician. His official, authorised
OL,8,Fbiography is laced with references to
OL,9,Fan MP devoted to God.
OL,11,FBut the truth could not have been more
OL,12,Fdifferent.
OL,14,FThe evidence given to his trial
OL,15,Frevealed a philandering politician
OL,16,Fhaving affairs at the same time as he
OL,17,Fwas leading prayers.His wife Eleanor
OL,18,FDonaldson was so convinced he had
OL,19,Fbetrayed her, she bugged his car.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
