OL,3,CJeffrey Donaldson's spectacular fall
OL,4,Cfrom grace
OL,6,FIn the witness box, Donaldson admitted
OL,7,Fto having one affair with a divorcee
OL,8,Fin London in 2008.
OL,10,FAt the time he was an MP, MLA, Junior
OL,11,FMinister at Stormont and a councillor.
OL,12,FHe had also just been sworn in as a
OL,13,FPrivy Councillor ` entitling him to be
OL,14,Fknown as the Right Honourable Jeffrey
OL,15,FDonaldson.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/5
