OL,3,CJeffrey Donaldson's spectacular fall
OL,4,Cfrom grace
OL,6,FBut even more damningly, this trial
OL,7,Fhas exposed the real Jeffrey Donaldson
OL,8,Fas a paedophile who had secretly
OL,9,Fabused young girls. He also denied
OL,10,Ftelling sinful and deceitful lies in
OL,11,Fcourt.
OL,13,FThe jury in Newry decided otherwise.
